data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-and-a-half-bath home in Waco, Texas. This residence has undergone an impressive transformation, reviving its original charm while incorporating modern updates. As you walk through the spunky, pink front door, you'll notice the large open living room that opens right into the kitchen and dining room! The kitchen has undergone a full renovation, including new granite countertops, new hardware, and brand new stove and oven! You'll also find a huge laundry room and pantry that opens up to the 2 car garage. Down the hallway, you'll find 2 bedrooms and full bath that has recently been updated and the master suite. All of the carpet in the bedrooms were newly installed this year, as well as beautiful luxury vinyl planking throughout the remainder of the home. Don't miss the amazing patio in the backyard to enjoy your morning coffee and sit back and relax. You won't want to miss this beauty! It is priced to sell!
